&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;This is the story of the fascinating journey of a Torah scroll which was&amp;#160;made in Spain in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color: #3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;the 14th or 15th century, &amp;#160;travelled to Rhodes with the Jewish exiles from Spain, was hidden during the Nazi occupation in a Muslim mosque, and was brought to the National Library of Israel by descendants of the community of Rhodes in 1999. &amp;#160;&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;
